Which of the following commands displays account information such as expiration date, lastpassword change, and other related details?
A)  usermod - l
B)  userinfo - a
C)  chageuser - l
D)  chage - l
D
D. The chage command is used for working with account aging information such as expi-ration date, password change, days between password changes, and so on. The - l commandlists information for the given account. The usermod command is used to make changes toan account, and the other two commands are not valid.
